data.description: **2.75% ASSUMABLE VA LOAN**Lovingly maintained one level charmer with 3 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms (both w/water saver toilets!), offering comfort and convenience! The inviting living area flows easily to the kitchen which features granite countertops, stainless appliances (NEW fridge and microwave; water heater, too!), and ample cabinet space. Need an area for office, home school, rec area, or to accommodate guests? It's here! Summer's upon us and the backyard oasis with an above ground pool and expansive deck for gatherings won't disappoint! Situated on a corner lot just over half an acre, there's plenty of space in both the front yard and fenced backyard. Follow the paved drive around back to a huge 2 car garage/workshop. A hop and a skip to MCAS New River, Yopp Rd shopping, easy access to the bypass, and less than 30 minutes to Topsail Beach. Don't miss this sweet location in southwest Jacksonville!
